      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:27:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 退出市场七年后重返夏威夷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/coinbase-returns-to-hawaii-seven-years-after-exiting-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过七年的缺席，Coinbase Global Inc. 表示将恢复向夏威夷居民提供加密服务，夏威夷是其唯一没有运营的州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/coinbase-returns-to-hawaii-seven-years-after-exiting-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国汽车工人联合会抓住唐纳德·特朗普赞扬伊隆·马斯克解雇工人的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uaw-seizes-on-donald-trump-praising-elon-musk-for-firing-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全美汽车工人联合会 (UAW) 猛烈抨击前总统唐纳德·特朗普对埃隆·马斯克对待其公司员工所采取的策略的称赞，并将这些言论转化为反对共和党候选人的信息，称工会将瞄准一个关键的选民选区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uaw-seizes-on-donald-trump-praising-elon-musk-for-firing-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 15:33:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Shein 聘请前欧盟官员加强 IPO 游说工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/shein-hires-former-eu-official-to-bolster-lobbying-as-ipo-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Shein 聘请了一位前欧盟高级官员来加强其在该地区的游说力度，并在计划在伦敦股票市场首次亮相之际，对潜在的监管审查采取更积极的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/shein-hires-former-eu-official-to-bolster-lobbying-as-ipo-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 15:24:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Mercuria 招聘前 IXM 铅锌部门负责人，助力金属行业招聘热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/mercuria-adds-former-ixm-lead-and-zinc-chief-in-metals-hiring-spree</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩科瑞能源集团有限公司 (Mercuria Energy Group Ltd.) 正在聘用竞争对手 IXM SA 的前铅锌业务主管，这是该公司近几个月来大力进军金属行业的最新高层任命。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/mercuria-adds-former-ixm-lead-and-zinc-chief-in-metals-hiring-spree</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:37:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡海运前景好，抵御 TikTok 和 Lazada</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/singapore-s-sea-tops-profit-estimates-on-online-shopping-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sea Ltd. 上调了其主要在线零售部门的业绩展望，表明这家东南亚电商领袖正面临来自 TikTok 和 Lazada 等公司的激烈竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/singapore-s-sea-tops-profit-estimates-on-online-shopping-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:41:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰“储物柜之王”就虚假广告和图片问题与 Meta 展开对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/meta-faces-legal-challenge-from-polish-billionaire-over-fake-ads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰亿万富翁拉法尔·布尔佐斯卡 (Rafal Brzoska) 正在发起一场运动，要求 Meta Platforms Inc. 对其社交网络应用程序上传播的虚假图片和欺诈性广告负责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/meta-faces-legal-challenge-from-polish-billionaire-over-fake-ads</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 08:13:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员希望 Alphabet 的 Pixel 活动能阻止 3600 亿美元的崩盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/traders-hope-alphabet-s-pixel-event-can-stem-360-billion-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 的投资者正焦急地等待周二的谷歌硬件发布会——依靠新的人工智能功能来帮助阻止这场在短短一个月内就导致市值蒸发超过 3600 亿美元的抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/traders-hope-alphabet-s-pixel-event-can-stem-360-billion-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 07:20:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国能源监管机构批准 34 亿英镑电力“高速公路”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uk-s-ofgem-signs-off-on-3-4-billion-electricity-superhighway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国能源监管机构英国天然气与电力市场办公室（Ofgem）批准了一项 34 亿英镑（44 亿美元）的融资计划，用于在北海下方建设一条电力“高速公路”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uk-s-ofgem-signs-off-on-3-4-billion-electricity-superhighway</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 06:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
